		<title>15The Future</title>
		<content>   What of the future?Todmorden's      
 traditional manufacturing base has    
 almost disappeared and new industry is
 restricted by the geography of the    
 area.Unemployment is above the        
 national average and the town has a   
 very high percentage of elderly       
 residents for whom more and more      
 provision will be require.On an       
 optimistic note,is following the lead 
 of neighbouring Hebden Bridge by      
 promoting the natural features and    
 traditional buildings as tourist      
 attractions.                          
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
